Travel - Class in Scheduling.ScheduleOptions
Holds the object for when the truck is traveling from one location to another with the knowledge that both the to and from can both be either the store front or the distributor, and finding the distance and direction for the traveling to take place

This is the constructor for the travel object which signifies that the truck has moved from location to another with the following associated information about the travel
TravelForm - Class in FormFiles.ScheduleForms
This class is used by the user to be able to add a travel object changing the trucks current location allow for the viewing stats around the travel selection and filtering travel options to only show the distributors and the store fronts that have loaded cargo as these are the only two locations to go to
